  <body>
    <h1>SOW with developer</h1>
    <h2>Steps to follow to ensure a successful partnership with a first time contractor</h2>
      <ol>Steps</ol>
        <li>Development of SOW (statement of work)</li>
          <ul>
            <li>Work to be accomplished</li>
            <li>Timeline, inclusive of check-ins</li>
            <li>If in a sprint format, should include a weekly understanding of sprint accomplishments, challenges, delays, impact of delays on original scope</li>
            <li>Fee structure and payment terms..net 30, net 45</li>
          </ul>
        <li>Review of SOW and signature</li>
        <li>Development of PO or just pay out of pocket</li>
        <li>External kick off call</li>
          <ul>
            <li>Workstyle, nights, mornings</li>
            <li>Communication style, text, email, phone, slack</li>
            <li>Schedule weekly check-ins and stress their importance</li>
          </ul>
        <li>Project commences</li>
        <li>Management of project during it</li>
        <li>Project completetion</li>

        <p>Project is complete and contractor should be paid within payment terms</p>
  </body>
  </html>
